---
title: Character Create Flow
---
flowchart TD
    A["!cstart : Start character creation"]
    B["!croll : Roll attributes (3d6x5 for each stat)"]
    C["!cjob &lt;job_name&gt; : Select a job and gain initial skills"]
    D["!cskill &lt;skill_name&gt; &lt;value&gt; : Allocate skill points"]
    E["!cbuy &lt;item_name&gt; : Purchase an item and add it to inventory"]
    F["!cmeta &lt;name&gt; : Finalize and save the character"]
    G["!cstatus : Show current character creation status"]

    A --> B
    B --> C
    C --> D
    D --> E
    E --> F
    F --> G
    G --> END((" "))
